/*
THIS STYLE IS OBSOLETE. If you are reading this,
decline to install it and instead use this addon;
https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/download-youtube/

While I am glad you've been using this style, this particular addon
had always been shady and underhanded in what functions you get.
The addon URL provided leads to something better, and more up-to-date.

Easy YouTube Video Downloader button CSS 0.5
By there.is.only.xul

Changelog:
0.1 - Initial release; Default button decoration only
0.5 - Second release; Added :focus and :hover pseudoclasses for better
      integration with the YouTube interface, looks less crappy.

Planned changes (since 0.5):
Add blue aura like on Share button, if possible, low urgency
Potentially resolve the bug issue with clicking Share first, then Download, wishlist urgency
*/

@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);
@-moz-document domain("youtube.com") ,url-prefix(http://www.youtube)
{
#download-youtube-video-button
{
/* All colors listed here are standard for YouTube -- Modify for themes if applicable */
border-top-color: rgb(204, 204, 204) !important;
border-bottom-color: rgb(170, 170, 170) !important;
border-right-color: rgb(204, 204, 204) !important;
border-left-color: rgb(204, 204, 204) !important;
background-color: rgb(224, 224, 224) !important;
box-shadow: 0px 0px 1px rgb(255, 255, 255) inset !important;
background-image: -moz-linear-gradient(center top , rgb(250, 250, 250) 0px , rgb(220, 220, 220) 100%) !important;
color: rgb(83,83,83) !important;
text-shadow: 0px 1px 0px rgb(255, 255, 255) !important;
}

#download-youtube-video-button:hover
{
border-top-color: rgb(170, 170, 170) !important;
border-right-color: rgb(170, 170, 170) !important;
border-bottom-color: rgb(153, 153, 153) !important;
border-left-color: rgb(170, 170, 170) !important;
box-shadow: 0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25), 0px 0px 3px rgb(255, 255, 255) inset !important;
background-image: -moz-linear-gradient(center top , rgb(240, 240, 240) 0px, rgb(230, 230, 230) 100%) !important;
}

#download-youtube-video-button:focus
{
border-right-color: rgb(170, 170, 170) !important;
border-left-color: rgb(170, 170, 170) !important;
border-bottom-color: rgb(204, 204, 204) !important;
border-top-color: rgb(153, 153, 153) !important;
box-shadow: 0px 1px 2px rgb(170, 170, 170) inset !important;
background-image: -moz-linear-gradient(center top , rgb(230, 230, 230) 0px, rgb(220, 220, 220) 100%) !important;
}
}
